    ======================================================================
    Affine variety point counting over F_2
    ======================================================================
    Over F_2: variety V_x with #V_x(F_2) = pi(x) is equivalent to
    finding a GF(2) circuit of poly(N) size computing the COUNT pi(x).
    This is the NC question over GF(2).
    
    x=100, pi(x)=25, F_2: min dimension d=5, N=7
    x=100, pi(x)=25, F_3: min dimension d=3, N=7
